## preheat oven
190 C

## ingredients
125 g all-purpose flour
3/4 tsp salt
1/2 tsp baking soda

57 g butter
1/4 tsp cinnamon 
113 g vegetable oil

82 g brown sugar
55 g white sugar

1 egg (+ 1 egg yolk if feeling fancy)
1 tsp vanilla

250-270 g rolled oats
handfull of other toppings (choco, nuts, raisins)

## brief instructions
1. mix dry ingredients in medium bowl
2. in separate pan: brown butter
3. transfer butter to large metal bowl; add cinnamon, vegetable oil, sugars, and beat in egg and vanilla
4. add dry into wet 
5. add oats and other toppings

## bake for
approx 10 min, until slightly underdone (edges set, center soft). 
